### Webhook: Account Creation Success
POST https://jpfxxoflclkpqsibvdil.supabase.co/functions/v1/unipile-webhook
Content-Type: application/json
x-unipile-webhook-secret: {{webhook_secret}}

{
  "status": "CREATION_SUCCESS",
  "account_id": "HZ5ydcdSTAiVWl8UrV11VA",
  "name": "badcea38-fbb2-45cf-9314-88771b63f42d"
}

### Webhook: Account Reconnected
POST https://jpfxxoflclkpqsibvdil.supabase.co/functions/v1/unipile-webhook
Content-Type: application/json
x-unipile-webhook-secret: {{webhook_secret}}

{
  "status": "RECONNECTED",
  "account_id": "HZ5ydcdSTAiVWl8UrV11VA",
  "name": "badcea38-fbb2-45cf-9314-88771b63f42d"
}

### Check existing account by unipile_account_id
GET https://jpfxxoflclkpqsibvdil.supabase.co/rest/v1/accounts?or=(unipile_account_id.eq.{{account_id}},proxy_settings->>external_id.eq.{{account_id}})
apikey: {{supabase_key}}

### Create account in Supabase (webhook)
POST https://jpfxxoflclkpqsibvdil.supabase.co/rest/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Prefer: return=representation
apikey: {{supabase_key}}

{
  "id": "{{account_id}}",
  "user_id": "{{user_id}}",
  "name": "LinkedIn",
  "status": "Ativo",
  "initials": "LI",
  "unipile_account_id": "{{account_id}}"
}

### Update account in Supabase (webhook)
PATCH https://jpfxxoflclkpqsibvdil.supabase.co/rest/v1/accounts?id=eq.{{existing_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{supabase_key}}

{
  "status": "Ativo",
  "unipile_account_id": "{{account_id}}"
}
